olicemen have been infected in Province 2, 55 in Bagmati Province, 87 in Gandaki Province, 78 in Province 5, 37 in Karnali Province and 13 in Far Western Province.\n\nSo far, a total of 41,649 people have been infected in Nepal and 23,290 have recovered. Similarly, 251 people died from coronavirus, according to the Ministry of Health and Population.","title":"1,954 police personnel test positve for COVID-19 - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/03/124687/","video":[]}
